### Description of Issue/Question
With some packages using the pkg.install module reports failure and returns an error code when the package actually successfully installed.

### Setup
I have noticed this happening with rubyinstaller_64 and chocolatey, as well as install packages I have written myself.

Here's an example, the output is fairly self-contradictory:

